We are using YAGSL for our swerve drive and thrifty encoders. The absolute encoders are definitely connected and being read as the wheels are properly aligning themselves when driving, however, the values are not being printed to the smart dashboard. The Gyroscope we are using is properly being printed onto the smartdashboard by YAGSL, however the encoder and other values like the setpoint are not being printed.

// Configure the Telemetry before creating the SwerveDrive to avoid unnecessary objects being created.
SwerveDriveTelemetry.verbosity = TelemetryVerbosity.HIGH;
